character.name: Lyra, young woman 20-25 years old, laboratory experiment subject/survivor. Short white hair with cyan blue streak on right side. Pale skin from long confinement. Light blue eyes, determined but tired expression. Wearing modified grey laboratory jumpsuit (half-technical, half-improvised) with tech armbands and straps. Glowing blue badge on chest. Reinforced dark boots. Subtle cables/sensors on suit. Athletic build, ready posture. Sci-fi laboratory setting, experimental tone. Color palette: grey, light blue, white, very limited dark red accents.
